pageContext.claim: “If you look, countries all over the world are exploding right now -- people that you said were doing a wonderful job, so wonderful. But right now, take a look at the countries that are exploding: You have Italy back. You have Spain back. You have France back. You have Germany back. You have a lot of countries, and that's not to knock them.”
pageContext.analysis: Compared to the United States, these countries were not "exploding" with coronavirus cases at the time.
